headline: Why Starbucks Stock Fell 18% in April
summary: Starbucks stock fell sharply on the "Liberation Day" tariffs announcement.  The stock fell again at the end of the month after missing the mark in its earnings report.  CEO Brian Niccol says the recovery is on track.
